7️⃣ What is Thymeleaf?
Server-side template engine.
Used to create dynamic HTML.
Works with Spring Boot.
HTML + dynamic data.

8️⃣ Thymeleaf File Location
src/main/resources/templates/

Example:

index.html
home.html

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

9️⃣ Thymeleaf Syntax
Display Data
<p th:text="${name}"></p>

Output:
Jatin

Variables
${variableName}

Set Attribute

<a th:href="@{/home}">Home</a>
----------------------------------------------------------

Conditional
<p th:if="${age > 18}">Adult</p>
<p th:unless="${age > 18}">Adult</p>

-----------------------------------------------------------

Loop
<ul>
  <li th:each="user : ${users}" 
      th:text="${user}">
  </li>
</ul>

-----------------------------------------------------------

🔟 Controller + Thymeleaf Full Flow
Browser sends request.
Controller receives request.
Controller prepares data.
Data added to Model.
Thymeleaf template loads.
HTML generated.
Response sent to browser.

